body_html:
@poxvoculi Hi, I may have not been precise. I only indicated the possibility it is not the computations that slow it down, but the data processing part. I am not sure how to benchmark it, because from the user point of view sess.run() does both compute and data feeding, so I cannot evaluate them individually. I use GPU version and not CPU, and in both cases (TF 1.2 and 1.3) I use pre-combiled builds, so it's comparable setting.

@ppwwyyxx I'll try to narrow down the the issue..
